                    <div class="homepagecol1">
                    	<h1>FACT SHEETS</h1>
                        <h2>Up-to-Date Review of the Major Issues</h2>
                        <div class="art">
                        	<a href="/facts-prolif"><img src="/images/prolif-icon.jpg" /></a>
                            <h3>Nuclear Proliferation</h3>
                            <p>While the immediate focus of international attention has been on stopping Iran from obtaining nuclear weapons, equally worrisome is the stimulated regional race for nuclear power.</p>
                            <p>Already, at least 12 other Muslim countries has announced plans to explore nuclear energy.</p>
                            <div class="detail_button_33"><a href="/facts-prolif">LEARN MORE</a></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="art">
                        	<a href="/facts-defense"><img src="/images/dome-icon.jpg" /></a>
                            <h3>Israeli Missile Defense</h3>
                            <p>The proliferation of rockets and ballistic missiles across the Middle East has forced Israel to strengthen its active anti-missile technology.</p>
                            <p>In response, Israel has created a multi-layered missile defense apparatus considered one of the most advanced in the world.</p>
                            <div class="detail_button_33"><a href="/facts-defense">LEARN MORE</a></div>
